<pb facs="1079253" n="1"/>
<opener><salute><choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimo</expan></choice> atque <choice><abbr>Celeberr.<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Celeberrimo</expan></choice> Viro
             <lb/><choice><abbr>J.</abbr><expan>Johanni</expan></choice> Bernoull
             <lb/>Petrus Antonius <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="peson">Michelottus</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Optatas tandem diuque a me expectatas a Te, Vir Prclarissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>me, accepi <rs key="B_1721-07-30_991170515149905501" type="letter">litteras</rs><note type="editorial">Meint den letzten Brief vom 30. Juli 1721 von Johann I Bernoulli an Michelotti</note>, ex iisque intellexi fascicul meor <rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">libro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>rum</rs> jam ad vestras pervenisse manus. Doleo de sumptibus quos face<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>re debuisti pro illo ipso fasciculo, contra ac jusseram. Rogaram enim <choice><abbr>Illustriss.</abbr><expan>Illustrissimam</expan></choice> Marchion <rs key="" type="person">Butintrochi</rs> ut mitteret ita ut nihil
             <lb/>tibi erogand esset. Sed statim ac <choice><abbr>Cl.</abbr><expan>Clarissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filius</rs> Tuus ex agro <rs key="place_GEO-3165243" type="place">Tridentino</rs>
<lb/>huc redierit ei persolv (quod justissim est) duos, quos solvisti flore<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>nos. Mihi enim grave est quod commercium me <choice><sic>epistolare</sic><corr>epistolarem</corr></choice>
<lb/>sit Tibi sumptuos, ideoque <choice><abbr>Cl.</abbr><expan>Clarissimo</expan></choice> Filio Tuo <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Nicolao</rs> restituam semper
             <lb/>qu pro meis litteris accipiendis, tuisque ad me mittendis solve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>re debebis. De hac re nihil, Vir <choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rendition="#sup">e</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissime</expan></choice>, dubitare debes. Ceter
             <lb/>spero Te, Prfation non tant ad me <rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">de <choice><abbr>Separ.<hi rendition="#sup">ne</hi>atione</abbr><expan>Separatione</expan></choice> Fluidor</rs>
<lb/>opus, sed et e quam Tuis doctissimis <rs key="biblio_W6BHQDM2 biblio_JAFFCHKU" type="biblios">Dissertationibus</rs> prmi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>si, Lectur, quod vehementer opto. Iust erat de Te quam ho<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>norificentissime verba facere, idque si displicebit Anglis<note type="editorial">Evtl. recherchieren, um wen es sich konkret handelt.</note>, eos
             <lb/>flocci faci. Ceter <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newton</rs> quoque <choice><abbr>celeberr.</abbr><expan>celeberrimum</expan></choice> Geometram
             <lb/>honorificentissime semper nominavi, uti me evolven<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>do opus videre poteris. Prstantissim Fili Tu <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Nicolaum</rs>
<lb/>una cum <choice><abbr>Ill.</abbr><expan>Illustrissimo</expan></choice> atque <choice><abbr>Excell.</abbr><expan>Excellentissimo</expan></choice> Viro <rs key="pers_DE-588-121710742" type="person"><choice><abbr>Jo.</abbr><expan>Johanne</expan></choice> Vezzi</rs> salv ad <rs key="place_WEI-disole" type="place"><choice><sic>Val</sic><corr>Vall</corr></choice> Solis</rs> in
             <lb/>agro <rs key="place_GEO-3165243" type="place">Tridentino</rs> jam pervenisse certo scio, eumque brevi
             <lb/>huc reditur Te admoneo. Credo ips ejusmodi aqu (qu
             <lb/>acidula est) nequaqu potasse: siquid id ego illi haud suasi.
             <lb/>Quando hinc discessit optima fruebatur valetudine, mi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>hi semper cordi erit ejus bona valetudo, eumque, uti si
             <lb/>esset meus Filius, custodire atque tueri Tibi Sancte promitto.</p>
<p><lb/>De iis, qu perdocte respondisti ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatian</rs> demonstration
         <lb/>attinentia hoc mihi a Te adhuc qurend restat. <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs>
<lb/>ideo scripsit, quantitatem aqu, tempore, quo grave altitudi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>nem <formula>IG</formula> confecit, egress qual esse <formula>EF\times2GI</formula>, quia de<pb facs="1079254" n="2"/>monstravit velocitat aqu representari jure posse per
         <lb/><formula>2GI</formula>, propterea quod aqu gutta velocitate acquisita
         <lb/>ex casu per <formula>GI</formula> motu uniformi eod tempore percurrere posset <formula>2GI</formula>.
         <lb/>Etenim spatia a mobili motu uniformi percursa
         <lb/>sunt ut velocitates. Poterit igitur fortasse respondere
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs>, ad id <rs key="B_1721-07-30_991170515149905501" type="letter">quod scripsisti</rs><note type="editorial">Zitiert aus: Johann I Bernoullis Brief vom 30.07.1721</note> <hi rendition="#u">producatur <formula>GI</formula> surs ad
            <lb/><formula>Z</formula> ita ut <formula>GZ</formula> sit <formula>=4GI</formula></hi>, non licere producere usque
         <lb/>ad <formula>Z</formula> in casu <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtoni</rs>, quia <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtonus</rs> videtur sume<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>re <formula>IH</formula> (vid. illius libr pag. 303<choice><orig>.</orig><reg>,</reg></choice> 2. edit.<note type="editorial">https://www.e-rara.ch/zut/content/pageview/338955</note>) uti lineol indefinite parv, et <formula>KL</formula> ut infinite proxim line <formula>AB</formula>.
         <lb/><unclear>Ad</unclear> id igitur, quod scribis<choice><orig>.</orig><reg>:</reg></choice> <hi rendition="#u">Sed moles aqu dato illo tempo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>re egress est qualis cylindro, cujus basis <formula>EF</formula> altitudo vero
            <lb/><formula>4GI</formula>,vel <formula>GZ</formula>(uti modo demonstrat est)</hi>: ad illud,
         <lb/>inqu, respondere posset <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs>, quomodo demonstrasti mol
         <lb/>aqu dato illo tempore egress esse <formula>EF\times4GI</formula>. N si ego dixi
         <lb/>(posset dicere <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs>) esse mol aqu illo tempore egress qua<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>l <formula>EF\times2GI</formula> ideo dixi, quia demonstravi, velocitat aqu
         <lb/>representari posse per <formula>2GI</formula>. <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccato</rs> igitur nobis demonstran<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>d est eod jure nos representare posse ill, de qua
         <lb/>loquimur velocitat, per <formula>4GI</formula> potius qu per <formula>2GI</formula>. Rogo ut eti
         <lb/>de hac, qu fieri potest, objectio, aliquid quamprim
         <lb/>ad me rescribas. Tota en <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccati</rs> demonstratio consistit in
         <lb/>hoc quod velocitas aqu exilientis debeat representari per
         <lb/><formula>2GI</formula>, quia motu uniformi tempore, quo descripsit motu accele<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>rato line <formula>GI</formula>, posset describere <formula>2GI</formula>.</p> <closer><salute>Vale, Vir <choice><abbr>Celeberr.<hi rendition="#sup">e</hi></abbr><expan>Celeberrime</expan></choice>, et
            <lb/>ad me respondere ne graveris, quso.</salute> <dateline><choice><abbr>D</abbr><expan>Dabam</expan></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice>
<lb/><date when="1721-08-08">8 Augusti 1721.</date></dateline></closer>
<pb facs="1079255" n="3"/>
<postscript><p>P. S.
             <lb/>Salut plurimam mitto <choice><abbr>Ill<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimo</expan></choice> Agnato Tuo <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao</rs><supplied>.</supplied></p></postscript>
